subject: WELCOME TO FEDEX DELIVERY COMP
body:

or bitcoin wallet ok

Agent :EMEKA A.GODWIN

subject: Re: WELCOME TO FEDEX DELIVERY COMP
body:
Hello Diplomatic,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I'm quite surprised to hear about this large sum of money. Can you please explain how my name ended up on the foreign debts settlement payment file? 

Also, could you provide more details about the different options for receiving the funds? I'm not very familiar with bank wire transfers, online banking or ATM cards. 

Lastly, I'm a bit confused about the payment method you mentioned - gift card or bitcoin wallet. Could you clarify what this payment is for?

Looking forward to your response.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Judith
